cks heading into the fourth quarter, but the firm issued three semi stock downgrades Friday and said stock selection is critical at the moment.\n\nThe Semiconductor Analyst:\n\nAnalyst Vivek Arya issued the following ratings and price target changes:", "symbols": ["AMD", "AVGO", "CREE", "CRUS", "KLAC", "MCHP", "MRVL", "NVDA", "NVMI", "ON", "SNPS"], "updated_at": "2021-09-17T14:55:46Z", "url": "https://www.benzinga.com/analyst-ratings/analyst-color/21/09/22988086/bofa-downgrades-synopsys-cirrus-logic-cree-names-top-q4-semi-picks"}, {"author": "Lisa Levin", "content": "", "created_at": "2021-09-30T11:58:11Z", "headline": "4 Stocks Insiders Are Selling", "id": 23171949, "images": [{"size": "large", "url": "https://cdn.benzinga.com/files/imagecache/2048x1536xUP/images/story/2012/insider-selling_40.jpg"}, {"size": "small", "url": "https://cdn.benzinga.com/files/imagecache/1024x768xUP/images/story/2012/insider-selling_40.jpg"}, {"size": "thumb", "url": "https://cdn.benzinga.com/files/imagecache/250x187xUP/images/story/2012/insider-selling_40.jpg"}], "source": "", "summary": "When insiders sell shares, it indicates their concern in the company’s prospects or that they view the stock as being overpriced. Either way, this signals an opportunity to go short on the stock. Insider sales should not be taken as the only indicator for making an investment or trading decision. At best, it can lend conviction to a selling decision.", "symbols": ["AVGO", "BKE", "DRI", "SNV"], "updated_at": "2021-09-30T11:58:11Z", "url": "https://www.benzinga.com/news/21/09/23171949/4-stocks-insiders-are-selling"}, {"author": "Bill Haddad", "content": "", "created_at": "2021-09-30T13:07:39Z", "headline": "Perforce To Acquire BlazeMeter Continuous Testing Platform From Broadcom; Terms Not Disclosed", "id": 23174147, "images": [], "source": "", "summary": "", "symbols": ["AVGO"], "updated_at": "2021-09-30T13:07:39Z", "url": "https://www.benzinga.com/news/21/09/23174147/perforce-to-acquire-blazemeter-con